snippet.title: My Brother Rabbit Announce Trailer - Fall 2018 [Steam, Xbox One, PS4, Nintendo Switch]
snippet.description:
Available this fall on Steam, Xbox One, PS4, Nintendo Switch

My Brother Rabbit is a beautifully drawn point-and-click adventure set in a surreal world that mixes reality with a child’s imagination.

Learn more: https://mybrotherrabbit.com
Add to Steam Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/855640/My_Brother_Rabbit
